H3.text: According to the nursery rhyme, who lives on Drury Lane. Muffin Man

A4.text: The muffin man lives in Drury Lane.

A5.text: Victorian households had many of their fresh foods delivered, such as muffins, which were delivered door-to-door by a vendor known as a muffin man.

A6.text: The Muffin Man resided on Drury Lane, according to the famous nursery rhyme.
